---

<dd class="flex text-gray-900 sm:col-span-2 flex-col">
  <div class="">
    <p>
      Your icon must be <em>square</em> and at least 128px x 128px (we recommend
      500px x 500px). It may have any colour background, and should be uploaded as
      PNG or JPEG formats.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex mt-5">
    <span class="flex-grow">
      <div class="">
        <img
          class="border rounded-md h-16 w-16"
          src="/sessions/logo.svg"
          alt=""
        />
      </div>
    </span>
    <span class="text-sm ml-4 flex flex-shrink-0 space-x-4 items-center">
      <button
        type="button"
        class="rounded-md bg-white font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
        >Change</button
      >
      <span class="text-gray-300" aria-hidden="true">|</span>
      <button
        type="button"
        class="rounded-md bg-white font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
        >Remove</button
      >
    </span>
  </div>

  <div
    class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-normal mt-5 w-full rounded-lg leading-6"
  >
    <p>
      Please note, this should not be your full logo which usually contains text
      as it will be displayed to your customers alongside your public business
      name.
    </p>
  </div>
</dd>
